**Lumina Crash** is a [[[theme:bedrock|Bedrock]]]-based theme created by [[*user EstrellaYoshte]], for personal use.

To import this theme to your page, put the following text anywhere inside it:

> {{@@[[include :scp-wiki:theme:bedrock]]@@}}
> {{@@[[include :scp-wiki:theme:lumina]]@@}}

------

Lumina Crash is generally not meant for easy, drop-in use â€” it may break layouts for some pre-existing components.

{{#page-content}} has been converted into grid layout, with the following column tracks:

[[div style="background-color: #00ff3644; padding: .15rem 1rem; border-inline: dashed green .175rem; margin-top: 1rem; text-align: center"]]
{{content}}
[[/div]]
[[div class="breakout-start" style="background-color: #c5ff0044; padding: .15rem 1rem; border-inline: dashed yellow .175rem;"]]
{{breakout-start}}
[[/div]]
[[div class="breakout-end" style="background-color: #c5ff0044; padding: .15rem 1rem; border-inline: dashed yellow .175rem; text-align: end"]]
{{breakout-end}}
[[/div]]
[[div class="breakout" style="background-color: #ffd10044; padding: .15rem 1rem; border-inline: dashed yellow .175rem; text-align: center"]]
{{breakout}}
[[/div]]
[[div class="full-width-start" style="background-color: #ff730044; padding: .15rem 1rem; border-inline: dashed red .175rem;"]]
{{full-width-start}}
[[/div]]
[[div class="full-width-end" style="background-color: #ff730044; padding: .15rem 1rem; border-inline: dashed red .175rem; text-align: end"]]
{{full-width-end}}
[[/div]]
[[div class="full-width" style="background-color: #ff120044; padding: .15rem 1rem; border-inline: dashed red .175rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; text-align: center"]]
{{full-width}}
[[/div]]

By default, children of {{#page-content}} live in the content zone. To change grid tracks, add the stated classes respectively.

For maximum compatibility to use as a normal theme, you can contain everything in a wrapper div, optionally with the above classes. Otherwise, expect a lot of manual styling.

